PN,30401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777306270
OL,3,CMore than 100 children's toys recalled
OL,4,Cover asbestos risk since January
OL,6,FDozens of children's toys containing
OL,7,Fsand have been recalled from stores
OL,8,Facross the UK due to risk of asbestos
OL,9,Fcontamination.
OL,11,FMore than 100 products, including sand
OL,12,Fart activity kits, stretcher toys, and
OL,13,Fa candle-making set, were pulled from
OL,14,Fshops between January and April this
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FThe Entertainer, Early Learning
OL,18,FCentre, Aldi, Hobbycraft, Morrisons,
OL,19,FMatalan, B&M, and Tesco are among the
OL,20,Fstores where the toys were being sold.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777306270
OL,3,CMore than 100 children's toys recalled
OL,4,Cover asbestos risk since January
OL,6,FCustomers are being urged to check
OL,7,Ftheir purchases and if they discover
OL,8,Fthey've bought any of the items, to
OL,9,Fstop using them immediately.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,F"It is staggering toys are being sold
OL,17,Fwith asbestos, and I know how
OL,18,Fconcerning this will be for parents,"
OL,19,FMinister for Product Safety Kate
OL,20,FDearden told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777306270
OL,3,CMore than 100 children's toys recalled
OL,4,Cover asbestos risk since January
OL,6,F"We're taking action with new measures
OL,7,Fto strengthen consumer protection and
OL,8,Fclamp down on irresponsible sellers.
OL,10,F"Our product safety laws are clear `
OL,11,Fbusinesses must ensure the products
OL,12,Fthey sell are safe and act when they
OL,13,Fhave sold unsafe products to consumers.
OL,15,F"We work closely with the EU, Trading
OL,16,FStandards and the toy industry to
OL,17,Fensure businesses act immediately, and
OL,18,Fany products which test positive for
OL,19,Fasbestos are removed from sale and
OL,20,Frecalled."
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
